# and routes the outcome via on_complete. Whether the card reaches `review`
# depends on the sandbox LLM completing in time, so the forward-progress steps
# are non-deterministic in CI (same class as review-panel-discussion). The
# workflows/tasks module is covered deterministically by the server unit suite
# (rest/workflows, rest/tasks, mcp) and the smoke tests.
orchestrate-a-sonnet-with-workflows
